{%- comment -%} Refund policy — for /pages/refund-policy {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="wa-page wa-page--legal wa-section--bleed" aria-labelledby="wa-refund-title">
  <div class="wa-aurora" aria-hidden="true"><div class="wa-aurora__blob"></div></div>
  <div class="wa-grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="wa-container wa-page__inner">
    <div class="wa-page__hero">
      <span class="wa-eyebrow">{{ 'wa.refund.eyebrow' | t }}</span>
      <h1 id="wa-refund-title" class="wa-page__title">
        {{ 'wa.refund.title_a' | t }} <span class="wa-gradient-text">{{ 'wa.refund.title_b' | t }}</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="wa-page__lede">
        {{ 'wa.refund.lede' | t }}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wa-page__layout">
      <article class="wa-prose wa-page__article">

        <h2>1. How to ask for a refund</h2>
        <p>
          Email <a href="mailto:refund@weirdartist.io">refund@weirdartist.io</a>
          from the address you used at checkout, with the order number in
          the subject line. That&rsquo;s the whole process.
        </p>

        <h2>2. How long it takes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>We confirm by email within 1 business day.</li>
          <li>Shopify processes the refund to your original payment method within 1&ndash;3 business days.</li>
          <li>Your bank or card issuer may take an additional 5&ndash;10 days to show the credit.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. What gets refunded</h2>
        <p>
          The full purchase price. Taxes that we collected and remitted are
          included. Shopify&rsquo;s payment-processing fees are absorbed by
          us, not deducted from your refund.
        </p>

        <h2>4. After the refund</h2>
        <p>
          The license key associated with the order is deactivated. The
          installer continues to function only as a 14-day evaluation build.
          We don&rsquo;t reach into your machine and remove anything.
        </p>

        <h2>5. After the 30-day window</h2>
        <p>
          We still want to hear from you. Bug reports get fixed for free,
          missing-feature requests are added to the roadmap, and if the tool
          is genuinely broken for your case we will issue a goodwill refund
          past the window &mdash; just write in.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Bulk &amp; team licenses</h2>
        <p>
          The 30-day window applies to the order as a whole. If you bought
          several seats and only want to return some, that&rsquo;s fine
          &mdash; tell us how many in the email.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Chargebacks</h2>
        <p>
          Please email us first. We answer within 1 business day and
          refunding directly is faster, cleaner, and avoids the dispute fees
          that punish small studios. We have never refused a legitimate
          refund request.
        </p>

        <p class="wa-page__meta">
          <span>Effective: 24 April 2026</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>Last updated: 24 April 2026</span>
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
